@startuml
title All Arrow Types

participant A
participant B
participant C

A -> B : Synchronous message
A ->> B : Asynchronous message (thin)
A --> B : Dotted response
A -->> B : Dotted async

A ->x B : Lost message
A -\ B : Half arrow top
A -/ B : Half arrow bottom

A ->o B : Arrow with circle end
A o-> B : Circle at start

A <-> B : Bidirectional
A <--> B : Bidirectional dotted

A -[#red]> B : Colored arrow
A -[#blue]>> B : Colored async

' Different line styles
A -> B : Normal
A --> B : Dotted
A ->> B : Thin arrowhead
A -->> B : Dotted thin

' Short arrows (within same participant group)
A -> A : Self message

@enduml
